OL,6,FA drink driver who reached speeds of
OL,7,F100mph in a residential area before
OL,8,Fcausing a fatal crash has been jailed.
OL,9,FJonathon Hopkinson, 35, had been at a
OL,10,Frestaurant and was over the limit when
OL,11,Fhe collided with a car being driven by
OL,12,F22-year-old Alice Birchall in Leeds on
OL,13,F18 June 2022.JLeeds Crown Court heard
OL,14,FHopkinson, of Hollyshaw Lane, was seen
OL,15,Fon CCTV driving at "excessive speeds"
OL,16,Fin residential areas.
OL,18,FHe reached 100mph in a 30mph zone
OL,19,Fshortly before crashing into Miss
OL,20,FBirchall's Nissan Juke on Manston Lane.
