OL,6,FIn a statement given at Leeds Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Miss Birchall's sister Amy
OL,8,Fsaid: "The senseless death of Alice
OL,9,Fhas left a gaping hole in all of our
OL,10,Flives. We all miss her positivity. We
OL,11,Fall miss her beautiful face."JThe
OL,12,Fcourt heard Hopkinson's young daughter
OL,13,Fwas in his car at the time of the
OL,14,Fcrash and suffered cuts to her face, a
OL,15,Fbroken nose and a fractured eye
OL,16,Fsocket. Hopkinson was also injured and
OL,17,Fhad to be put into an induced coma.JHe
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving and causing injury
OL,20,Fby dangerous driving.
