OL,6,FAnna Duffy, a physiotherapist and
OL,7,Fpsychotherapist who said she had been
OL,8,Fdriven by Hopkinson before the
OL,9,Fincident, said: "This has affected him
OL,10,Fdeeply. He cannot remember the crash
OL,11,Fand cannot comprehend why he would
OL,12,Fdrive that way, especially with (his
OL,13,Fdaughter) in the car. It's mind
OL,14,Fboggling."JHopkinson was jailed for
OL,15,Feight years and banned from driving
OL,16,Ffor 12 years.
