OL,6,FJudge Tom Bayliss KC told him: "You
OL,7,Fchose to drive at grossly excessive
OL,8,Fspeeds for some considerable distance.
OL,9,F"The speeds showed on the CCTV is
OL,10,Fbreathtaking."
OL,12,FAfter the sentencing Det Con Lindsey
OL,13,FPickles, of West Yorkshire Police's
OL,14,FMajor Collision Enquiry Team, said:
OL,15,F"By taking to the wheel while over
OL,16,Flimit that night, Hopkinson's actions
OL,17,Fcaused the death of one young woman
OL,18,Fand untold devastation to her friend
OL,19,Fand family.
